g.ns0:text: Se adiciona la funci\xc3\xb3n\\\\\npupila generalizada al\\\\\ncampo $U(\\xi,\\eta)$\\\\\n$G(\\xi,\\eta)=P(\\xi,\\eta)U(\\xi,\\eta)$
Se toma transformada de\\\\\nFourier del campo $u$\\\\\n$U(\\xi,\\eta)=\\mathscr{F} \\{u(x,y)\\}$
Simulaci\xc3\xb3n de la pupila\\\\\ngeneralizada del sistema\\\\\n$P(\\xi,\\eta)=A_p(\\xi,\\eta)\\exp\\{ i H(\\xi,\\eta)\\}$
Se toma antitransformada de\\\\\nFourier del campo $G$\\\\\n$g(x,y)=\\mathscr{F}^{-1} \\{G(\\xi,\\eta)\\}$
